17:19.706 --> 17:21.749
'cause we love each other.

17:21.791 --> 17:23.376
Oh!

17:25.586 --> 17:27.797
We forgive you.

17:34.428 --> 17:36.973
See, now, who knew the kids

17:34.428 --> 17:36.973
could work this out

17:37.015 --> 17:39.350
