18:28.649 --> 18:30.484
I should have,

18:28.649 --> 18:30.484
but I was afraid

18:30.526 --> 18:32.486
you wouldn't

18:30.526 --> 18:32.486
let me see her again.

18:32.528 --> 18:35.782
But that's just fine

18:32.528 --> 18:35.782
with me.

18:35.823 --> 18:38.242
Well, Deej, I know I say

18:35.823 --> 18:38.242
a lot of things about Kimmy

18:38.284 --> 18:40.327
being an annoying,

18:38.284 --> 18:40.327
obnoxious nuisance

18:40.369 --> 18:42.872
