18:42.914 --> 18:45.332
...but she's still

18:42.914 --> 18:45.332
your best friend.

18:45.374 --> 18:47.418
If somebody

18:45.374 --> 18:47.418
makes a wrong choice

18:47.460 --> 18:48.836
I don't think you can just

18:48.878 --> 18:51.631
walk away from them

18:48.878 --> 18:51.631
