Yeah, well, I-I really

18:51.672 --> 18:53.424
don't wanna spend

18:53.466 --> 18:56.719
the rest of my life with Kimmy

18:53.466 --> 18:56.719
draped over my shoulder.

18:56.761 --> 18:59.430
She's just not the kind of

18:56.761 --> 18:59.430
person I wanna hang out with.

19:00.848 --> 19:03.726
Yeah, but you're the kind

19:00.848 --> 19:03.726
of person she needs.

19:03.768 --> 19:05.645
Especially now,

19:03.768 --> 19:05.645
don't you think?

