I thought you'd have

19:12.902 --> 19:14.862
made it home by now.

19:14.904 --> 19:16.906
I'm pacing myself.

19:16.948 --> 19:20.743
My objective

19:16.948 --> 19:20.743
is the fence by nightfall.

